high_descs: Turn left, walk in the corridor, walk straight towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, take the potato from the fridge, close it.
Turn around, walk straight, turn right, take left towards the sink back side.
Put the potato into the sink, wash it, take back the potato.
Turn right, move, turn left, move, turn left, walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the potato inside, close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To get the potato in the fridge, wash it, put back in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around turn right go straight to the fridge
Take the potato from the fridge
Turn left go straight turn right to the sink
Put the potato in to the sink and clean it
Turn left go straight turn right to the fridge
Place the potato on the fridge
anns.task_desc: Take the potato from the fridge and Place the potato on the fridge

high_descs: Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the fridge on your right
Pick up potato from the fridge
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the sink
Place potato inside the sink and then take it out
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the fridge
anns.task_desc: Washing potato on the sink and placing it on fridge
